name: Floral Garden at Sunrise #02
description:
The "Floral Garden at Sunrise #02" is one of several images in the "Colorful Floral Gardens NFT Series". It was created to depict the anticipated gardens of beautiful, colorful flowers soon to be in bloom with the coming of Spring. The series reflect natural gardens of wildflowers and backyard gardens at sunrise as well as sunset; along mountainsides, and on river banks. The image reflects an amazing color combination. 

The images in the "Colorful Floral Gardens NFT Series" were created with the assistance of artificial intelligence, VQGAN+CLIP (machine learning algorithms), and text prompts. The image may be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
